com.codename1.webrtc

Class AudioTrackConstraints

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.codename1.webrtc.MediaTrackConstraints
      • com.codename1.webrtc.AudioTrackConstraints
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JSONStruct

    public class AudioTrackConstraints
extends MediaTrackConstraints

    Defines audio constraints for a call to RTC.getUserMedia(com.codename1.webrtc.MediaStreamConstraints).

    See https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaTrackConstraints for information about WebRTC media track constraints.
